OL,6,FITV Border's Clare McNeill went down
OL,7,Fto the Open to meet some of the
OL,8,Fcompetitors
OL,10,FThe Borders is hosting Scotland's
OL,11,Ffirst Open for golfers with
OL,12,Fdisabilities at Cardrona Golf Resort
OL,13,Fnear Peebles.
OL,15,FMore than 40 players from across the
OL,16,FUK, Ireland, and Australia are
OL,17,Fcompeting in the two-day tournament
OL,18,Fwhich aims to showcase inclusivity
OL,19,Fwithin the sport.
