OL,6,FGolfers with a range of physical and
OL,7,Fmental impairments including amputees
OL,8,Fand paragolfers are taking part in the
OL,9,Fcompetition.
OL,11,FLifelong golfer Gordon McLay was
OL,12,Fstruggling to play the game after a
OL,13,Fmotorcycle accident in 2007 and
OL,14,Funderwent a below the knee amputation
OL,15,Ftwo years ago.
OL,17,F"Before my amputation I was playing in
OL,18,Fsevere pain," he said.
