OL,6,F"Ever since I've got a new life again
OL,7,FI'm loving it out on the golf course,
OL,8,Fbit of freedom and that's why it's an
OL,9,Fescape from me.
OL,11,F"When I get on the golf course, I
OL,12,Fdon't think of anything else, I'm just
OL,13,Fthinking about golf.
OL,15,F"Life's strains just disappear."
OL,17,FAdapted equipment such as mobility
OL,18,Fchairs and specially designed clubs
OL,19,Faim to create an equal playing field
OL,20,Ffor athletes with a whole range of
OL,21,Fabilities.
