OL,6,FRobbie Clyde, CEO of Scottish Gold
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's really important that we
OL,8,Fshowcase golf as as welcoming and
OL,9,Faccessible for everybody.
OL,11,F"We've got a really broad range of
OL,12,Fcompetitors with all kinds of
OL,13,Fdisability.
OL,15,F"The beauty of these events is they
OL,16,Fcan compete together on a level
OL,17,Fplaying field
OL,19,F"The quality of the players this week
OL,20,Fis outstanding.
